{"tid":1972014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃店之間有糾紛根本一d都唔出奇","createTime":"2020-04-14T09:21:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T15:35:59.000Z","uid":61886,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d86cc58142addcb4fa0b42fbe9faa2851b4d42ff","tid":1972014,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T09:21:47.000Z","msg":"我當黃既有200萬人<br />\n我都唔會話可以同200萬人都夾得黎<br />\n黃只係政治立場<br />\n性格、態度、品格都各有不同<br />\n大家都係黃 唔等如大家都一定唔會有爭執<br />\n200萬人自然會有200種聲音<br />\n<br />\n我只係堅信兩點<br />\n第一<br />\n黃店唔會因為有爭執或者有糾紛之後<br />\n之後變左做藍店<br />\n<br />\n第二<br />\n好好思考人地批評你既野<br />\n諗下點樣去改善<br />\n我地係不分化<br />\n但唔等如不改善<br />\n<br />\n如果繼續搬藍絲果套盲撐理論<br />\n我地未必可以一步一步行到而家<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以多獨立思考<br />\n連登咩人都有 五毛、假膠、真心膠等等"},{"pid":"e7f70296b3e9971c7b8f063b00ac88166a77b57c","tid":1972014,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T09:22:45.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"e12fa2f639ca6c52d090a28f329fc321ccb90591","tid":1972014,"uid":61886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e7f70296b3e9971c7b8f063b00ac88166a77b57c","tid":1972014,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T09:22:45.000Z","msg":"拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T09:27:46.000Z","msg":"OK"},{"pid":"adbce27b7d8a6d5e4de4f62913a063f6fec61622","tid":1972014,"uid":258784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T09:28:34.000Z","msg":"[即時生效]以後邊個再鬥黃就原地做一set體能<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1969685\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1969685</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b5d29621d4baa085cc3b9c9ab2d68ff115067562","tid":1972014,"uid":187987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T09:28:51.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"4c231ed03cc79932dddae1128929be2df4dd6dc1","tid":1972014,"uid":186363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T09:29:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16f3d0fda6a16a1856b88d5ebc322102a0efa9d8","tid":1972014,"uid":303450,"